{"tid":2488069,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本AV女優水瀨源的出道，通過她去了解業內那些少為人知的細節，一片收費高達....","createTime":"2021-04-14T03:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T04:47:29.000Z","uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e375dca0ab5cee2487148dfa05621e471444e637","tid":2488069,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"在日本成人電影界裡，女演員們大概分成3類，分別是單體，企畫單體，企畫，其中出場費最高，作品最少的被分為單體（也叫專屬），只佔總數的5 %<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F53c26374p00qrgaf000j0c000qs00etc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F53c26374p00qrgaf000j0c000qs00etc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=ec658662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  而我們今天要介紹的女演員名叫水瀨源，20歲，從今年秋開始，她正式從一名寫真偶像轉職成一名女演員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F27d0a387p00qrgaf000q0c000qw00f0c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F27d0a387p00qrgaf000q0c000qw00f0c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=d158b998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  面對鏡頭，水瀨並沒有繞圈，而她成為演員的理由很簡單，那就是有名發行商主動找她，而她直接表示，要不是專屬的免談！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F36f6bf27p00qrgaf000hfc000qv00exc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F36f6bf27p00qrgaf000hfc000qv00exc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=0c150072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  過去，水瀨還是一名少有名氣的地下偶像，在寫著偶像界也混得不錯，因此，找她拍攝的發行商一口就答應了她的要求，讓她成為專屬備受矚目<br />\n<br />\n  話說，水瀨平時最愛的事就是購物，在表參道裡，可謂是各路名店的&ldquo;常客&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F3c02e2aap00qrgaf100i9c000qo00euc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F3c02e2aap00qrgaf100i9c000qo00euc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=24c44850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  平時的她沒有什麼愛好，除了購物以外，就是在家發呆，不知道在幹嘛，但肯定肯定的是，一有時間她肯定外出，四處走走，除了有工作以外，基本上就是吃飯，購物，逛街，唱K<br />\n<br />\n  距離第一次拍攝還有24小時，天氣：雨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2Fbd2e359dp00qrgaf100ibc000qv00f8c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252Fbd2e359dp00qrgaf100ibc000qv00f8c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=22a3eeea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  水瀨表示：哪怕下雨也不會妨礙到我，因為我決定在拍攝前減肥！去健身~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2Fc47de45ep00qrgaf000h2c000qv00f9c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252Fc47de45ep00qrgaf000h2c000qv00f9c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=7d72c126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  健身完以後，事務所為她準備了一間高級酒店，據悉這是只有專屬女演員才會受到的特別待遇，其目的是平復心境用的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F1e7b42c5p00qrgaf100hnc000r000f2c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F1e7b42c5p00qrgaf100hnc000r000f2c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=df5b33df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  問：請問您現在的心境是如何的<br />\n<br />\n  水瀨：非常緊張！因為這是自己第一次拍攝電影啊....<br />\n<br />\n  專屬女演員的早上從來都是早的！時間：早上7點<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F4d972ce2p00qrgaf000gvc000qs00exc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F4d972ce2p00qrgaf000gvc000qs00exc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=b9f6dc41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  這時候水瀨已經開始化妝了<br />\n<br />\n  在拍攝現場裡，有非常多的攝影機，零食，以及攝影棚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F0a099c91p00qrgaf100lpc000qx00f0c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F0a099c91p00qrgaf100lpc000qx00f0c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=449d58b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  可以看出，這與一般拍攝的完全不是一個等級！（話說，此前我們介紹了一名企畫女優，她的待遇與水瀨相比，完全是一天一地啊！&ldquo;傳送門&rdquo;）"},{"pid":"57ed1921aad2d6da32c96c29785ff89b9b5a18ca","tid":2488069,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"一名正在用剪刀對衣服進行現場裁剪的男性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F19c64049p00qrgaf100grc000qw00exc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F19c64049p00qrgaf100grc000qw00exc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=81ba069c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  上前詢問後我們得知，他是業內有名的木村監督，他說，每次女演員用的衣服都是自己挑選後現場買過來的，然後會在現場對其二次修改，畢竟衣服非常重要！而且我們不想給他人賣廣告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2Fa64b37bap00qrgaf100k3c000qs00f4c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252Fa64b37bap00qrgaf100k3c000qs00f4c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=3001f8c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  同時，監督對攝影機的控制也非常高挑，要求準備多台大小不一的攝影機，以及相機，但你可別以為這是為了拍出不同效果，其主要原因是，大的攝影機會容易使女演員緊張，為了緩解情緒，他們會使用根據實際情況使用小體積攝影機或相機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F8f135fa8p00qrgaf000l6c000qr00eyc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F8f135fa8p00qrgaf000l6c000qr00eyc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=b9d4821d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  全部準備好以後就是拍照了，基本上2天內拍2500張，然後選其中的1張作為封面，監督表示，如果封面不好看，基本就沒人買賬了，而且專屬不可以過分PS，不然外裡不一，下次就基本賣不出了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F1216d4d1p00qrgaf000hac000r800f4c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F1216d4d1p00qrgaf000hac000r800f4c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=92c4ba9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  照片拍完以後，已經是下午4點了，水瀨也開始習慣這種氛圍！拍攝很快就會開始<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F072f8820p00qrgaf000f9c000qv00ezc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F072f8820p00qrgaf000f9c000qv00ezc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=641e988c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  而水瀨的初次拍攝的合作演員就是我們熟知的&ldquo;清水健，健哥！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  拍攝結束後，我們問健哥如何，對此健哥說：寶石箱，不愧是做過偶像的啊！前途無限啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F804c197dp00qrgaf000d6c000qu00ezc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F804c197dp00qrgaf000d6c000qu00ezc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=7133c220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  最後水瀨表示：雖然我不知道第三者的感想是怎麼樣的，不過既然我已經選了這條路，那就只好一路走下去<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F4125b89ep00qrgaf000bgc000qu00f1c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F4125b89ep00qrgaf000bgc000qu00f1c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=8d76f3ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  那麼問題來了，她這次的報酬是....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0412%2F37514cc6p00qrgaf100akc000qs00f3c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0412%252F37514cc6p00qrgaf100akc000qs00f3c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=be149548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  300萬日元！約合rmb18萬元！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  水瀨說：做地下偶像以及寫作偶像，根本不敢想像.....<br />\n<br />\n  對此，我們只能吐槽一下，怪不得日本現在這麼多地下偶像，寫作偶像跑去出道了...."},{"pid":"01399703de595c9242e190f95285c34018b6a6ee","tid":2488069,"uid":192465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:54:15.000Z","msg":"真係攞個閪做八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靠個閪主導自己人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2fe7517f345ca862fc081c1df961fcaecff89d","tid":2488069,"uid":138497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:56:04.000Z","msg":"麻麻地wo⋯⋯"},{"pid":"d43c68a7da1ebcda714b7c49b033e4ca6abec5e5","tid":2488069,"uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:57:19.000Z","msg":"又係健哥<br />\n食咁撚正女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢都就快50<br />\n個個都做得佢個女"},{"pid":"97f9a90926b7a60ae2001ac051e9e4f7c7379c4d","tid":2488069,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db2fe7517f345ca862fc081c1df961fcaecff89d","tid":2488069,"uid":138497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:56:04.000Z","msg":"麻麻地wo⋯⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"隻眼整到三眼皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家真係太多整容膠面女優 唔撚開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8b1600b2905e54f29dcb8aa2ff5ef239898b59","tid":2488069,"uid":184822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"健哥夠專業<br />\n有時肥婆都出到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9801c32ef215d7996403f1e6992b1516471a0d","tid":2488069,"uid":385460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:05:49.000Z","msg":"當wiki 咗清水健同睇過訪問佢嘅YouTube 後，清水大神真心堅......唔怪之得男優數量唔多，出名嘅得幾個......"},{"pid":"0a8c98212ca7c33b68bc55e702d6abc487ce5e26","tid":2488069,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f8b1600b2905e54f29dcb8aa2ff5ef239898b59","tid":2488069,"uid":184822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"健哥夠專業<br />\n有時肥婆都出到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:18:33.000Z","msg":"如果次次都係同青春偶像拍,男優就唔會得咁少人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50632114946b26b29b31d86687896197a958aba2","tid":2488069,"uid":197640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52afeb5f1331478e3c901352b6a30d89e587f939","tid":2488069,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"dmm 搵唔到"}]}